Class OrderMenu.Drink

java.lang.Object
OrderMenu.Drink
Enclosing class:
OrderMenu
static class OrderMenu.Drink extends Object
Drink object: Stores each row of the menu database in memory. Includes the id, name, category, price, stock, hot type, and ingrediants from the menu.

    • Drink

      public Drink(int id, String name, String category, double price, boolean in_stock, boolean option_hot, Array ingredients)
      Parameters:
      id - The id of the drink in the database
      name - The name of the drink
      category - The drink's category
      price - The drinks price, times 100,000. For example, 5.75 becomes 575000.
      in_stock - If the drink is currently in stock or not.
      option_hot - If the drink is hot.
      ingredients - The ingredients that go into the drink.
